  "1857080": {
    "name": "The Last Starship",
    "steam_appid": 1857080,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《最后的星舰》是一款2D太空建造与模拟游戏，您将设计并升级专属星际飞船。驾驶它探索生机勃勃的星系，发掘独特资源，揭开隐藏的秘密。您的选择塑造游戏体验——成为无畏的海盗猎手、机智的矿工、太空工程师、可靠的太空巴士司机，或开启更多职业！在这片不断扩展的沙盒宇宙中，潜入绚丽星系，并享受开发过程中的定期免费更新。你的宇宙征程才刚刚启航！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/a85097800700107ee91eec884b6f8e48.poster.avif?t=1770209693\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/a85097800700107ee91eec884b6f8e48.webm?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/a85097800700107ee91eec884b6f8e48.mp4?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/e24b1bb6ab41aad5451d194dcb075f97.webp?t=1770209693\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/509eaa3af77809e0bbc3b1679df2bcb2.poster.avif?t=1770209693\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/509eaa3af77809e0bbc3b1679df2bcb2.webm?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/509eaa3af77809e0bbc3b1679df2bcb2.mp4?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >船员已整装待命，是时候让你的星舰焕发生命力。打造天马行空的梦想飞船，或复刻经典影视作品中的传奇战舰。前往当地太空殖民地采购装备物资，先安装反应堆驱动引擎，再铺设关键管道与电力系统。维持生命支持系统稳定运转，否则旅程恐将戛然而止。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/487be6d441d58d2f521d12970f43b6c4.webp?t=1770209693\" width=600 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过Steam创意工坊的飞船共享功能，释放玩家社群的无限创造力。只要能构想，就能设计、分享，让他人驾驶你的杰作参与史诗级冒险与战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/ef88a8a6cd9d75f4cd277ef59629d6e8.webp?t=1770209693\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/bc8ea3b74585b4cc1ecb73177466eb52.poster.avif?t=1770209693\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/bc8ea3b74585b4cc1ecb73177466eb52.webm?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/bc8ea3b74585b4cc1ecb73177466eb52.mp4?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全面掌控星舰的武器库。是安装激光炮实现精准打击，还是配备电磁炮制造毁灭性冲击？偏爱重型装甲提升韧性，还是增强机动性以压制敌方？选择隐形模式悄然穿行，抑或堆砌火力主宰战场？《最后的星舰》不仅考验火力，更是战术思维的试炼场——每场遭遇战都需要周密部署、灵活应变与精准打击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/97d5d6168cbb2cce433b18beaf001c98.webp?t=1770209693\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/8819ee4020637552770a5c642d8e2c5e.poster.avif?t=1770209693\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/8819ee4020637552770a5c642d8e2c5e.webm?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/8819ee4020637552770a5c642d8e2c5e.mp4?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >星区地图开启通往生机勃勃的程序生成宇宙之门，其中充斥着任务、异常现象与意外发现。邂逅形形色色的角色——或为盟友，或为对手——他们各自拥有引人入胜的故事与求助请求。展开惊险营救，运送关键货物，追捕臭名昭著的海盗。每个抉择都将塑造你的航线，在充满奇观与危机的瞬息万变星系中，雕琢出独一无二的航程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/d355159e7fe020c7dd834df70a636813.webp?t=1770209693\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/52c6df497e17b19709c431d2304c2783.poster.avif?t=1770209693\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/52c6df497e17b19709c431d2304c2783.webm?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/52c6df497e17b19709c431d2304c2783.mp4?t=1770209693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >太空冰冷、黑暗且辽阔。为求生存，你必须收集水、氧气和燃料等关键资源，以维持飞船运转并保障船员生存。无论是派遣无人机打捞太空残骸，还是用激光为巨型采矿平台提取原材料，建立无缝衔接的运作体系至关重要。唯有如此，才能获取在深空生存所需的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857080/extras/b691b31c89b680986cfd0b8dc3395153.webp?t=1770209693\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《最后的星舰》（The Last Starship）是备受赞誉的独立游戏开发商 Introversion Software 的最新力作，该公司最知名的作品是荣获 BAFTA 大奖的《监狱建筑师》（Prison Architect）。游戏于 2026 年 2 月正式上线，并会根据玩家的反馈定期更新，包括新增任务、修复漏洞以及改进游戏玩法。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introversion Software 自 2001 年起便开始开发游戏，旗下拥有《Uplink》、《Darwinia》、《DEFCON》、《Multiwinia》和《Scanner Sombre》等众多广受好评的作品。我们最成功的游戏《监狱建筑师》于 2012 年开启抢先体验，吸引了超过四百万玩家，并在六年间进行了 54 次重大内容更新——平均每月一次。</p>",
